<item>
            <title>[HBASE-2673] Investigate consistency of intra-row scans</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-2673</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have an intuition that intra-row scanning probably does not provide a consistent view of the row. We should investigate how true this is, and document what the interaction of the feature is with the guarantee, etc.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
